{"data":[{"date":"07:01 02/07","title":"De Gea nh\u1eadn \"m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1\" sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f3 tin \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/de-gea-bi-nhan-mua-gach-da-sau-man-trinh-dien-kho-tin-o-world-cup-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1eebng c\u1ee9u thua 18 l\u1ea7n trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League nh\u01b0ng khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup, David De Gea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 2 pha c\u1ee9u thua trong 4 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. </h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1 sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1 sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/0.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">K\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi David De Gea. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Man Utd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m s\u01a1 \u0111\u1eb3ng m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ph</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1 sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f3 tin \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"De Gea nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1 sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f3 tin \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/De-Gea-nhan-mua-gach-da-sau-man-trinh-dien-kho-tin-o-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a&nbsp; \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 6 l\u1ea7n. M\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Akinfeev thuc hien 2 pha cuu thua chi tinh rieng trong loat sut luan luu voi Tay Ban Nha. Trong khi do, De Gea chi co 1 lan can pha thanh cong trong 4 tran dau tai World Cup 2018\" title=\"Akinfeev th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2 pha c\u1ee9u thua ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang trong lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, De Gea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/065558-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Trang Twitter ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a FIFA: Akinfeev th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2 pha c\u1ee9u thua ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang trong lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, De Gea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Co le Luis Suarez lam thu mon cho Tay Ban Nha se tot hon la De Gea, CDV OMAR lay pha choi bong bang tay cua Suarez tai World Cup 2010 de che nhao thu mon cua Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"C\u00f3 l\u1ebd Luis Suarez l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 De Gea, C\u0110V OMAR l\u1ea5y pha ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng tay c\u1ee7a Suarez t\u1ea1i World Cup 2010 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/4.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&quot;C\u00f3 l\u1ebd Luis Suarez l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 De Gea&quot;, C\u0110V c\u00f3 t\u00ean OMAR l\u1ea5y pha ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng tay c\u1ee7a Suarez t\u1ea1i World Cup 2010 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"World Cup nam nay giup chung ta hieu ra rang: De Gea co choi hay den dau cung khong bao gio du kha nang thay the huyen thoai Iker Casillas\" title=\"World Cup n\u0103m nay gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta hi\u1ec3u ra r\u1eb1ng: De Gea c\u00f3 ch\u01a1i hay \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iker Casillas\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/3_1.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">World Cup n\u0103m nay gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta hi\u1ec3u ra r\u1eb1ng: De Gea c\u00f3 ch\u01a1i hay \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iker Casillas</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea qua te hai. Toi se phai tiep tuc chung kien anh ta dung trong khung go cua Man Utd hang tuan 10 nam toi\" title=\"De Gea qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn anh ta \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Man Utd h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n 10 n\u0103m t\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/41.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Gea qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn anh ta \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Man Utd h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n 10 n\u0103m t\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Day la hinh anh David De Gea tai World Cup nam nay\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh David De Gea t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/5.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh David De Gea t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pha cuu thua tot nhat cua De Gea o World Cup 2018 co le la tinh huong anh ta bat gon chai nuoc tu dong doi trong gio nghi giai lao\" title=\"Pha c\u1ee9u thua t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a De Gea \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh ta b\u1eaft g\u1ecdn chai n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/6.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pha c\u1ee9u thua t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a De Gea \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh ta b\u1eaft g\u1ecdn chai n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Co the thay ro su khac biet giua phong do cua De Gea khi truoc mat anh khong phai la xe buyt Man Utd.\" title=\"C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a De Gea khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 xe bu\u00fdt Man Utd.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/11.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a De Gea khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 xe bu\u00fdt Man Utd.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"801","checkdouble":"190143"},{"date":"08:10 02/07","title":"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y G\u1ea5u Nga qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 B\u00f2 t\u00f3t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-gau-nga-quat-nga-bo-tot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luzhniki m\u1edf h\u1ed9i trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga.\r\n</h2><h2>Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup, \u0110T Nga \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, sau khi qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh. Trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, trung v\u1ec7 Sergei Ignashevich ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0, b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga v\u1eabn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n do c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dzyuba, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t qua 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh. Nga ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, r\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Igor Akinfeev x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng vinh danh, khi anh \u0111\u1ea9y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, \u0110T Nga s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110an M\u1ea1ch sau \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"C\u0110V Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-gau-nga-quat-nga-bo-tot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V Nga c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\